<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q40_v6" title="Q40_v6" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Una persona evalúa dos plataformas de streaming para ver películas durante un mes. El costo mensual depende de la cantidad de películas, que llamaremos <m:math><m:mi>n</m:mi></m:math>.</p>
    <p>Para calcular el costo total, en pesos, se usan las siguientes expresiones lineales:</p>
    <p>
      Plataforma 1:
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:msub><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msub>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mn>1400</m:mn>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>500</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mi>n</m:mi>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      <br />
      Plataforma 2:
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:msub><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mn>2600</m:mn>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mi>n</m:mi>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
    </p>
    <p>Se sabe que existe una cierta cantidad de películas para la cual el costo total mensual es el mismo en ambas plataformas. Si esa cantidad es <m:math><m:mi>n</m:mi></m:math>, ¿cuántas películas debe ver en ese mes para que ambos cobros sean iguales?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">2<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <strong><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></strong>, en la plataforma 1 el costo es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1400</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>500</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2400</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y en la plataforma 2 el costo es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2600</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2400</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>3200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, ambos cobros no son iguales.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">6<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si <strong><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></strong>, en la plataforma 1 el costo es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1400</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>500</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1400</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4400</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y en la plataforma 2 el costo es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2600</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2600</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1800</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4400</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4400</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4400</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, ambos cobros son iguales.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">4<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <strong><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></strong>, en la plataforma 1 el costo es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1400</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>500</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3400</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y en la plataforma 2 el costo es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2600</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3800</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3400</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>3800</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, ambos cobros no son iguales.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">20<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <strong><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></strong>, en la plataforma 1 el costo es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1400</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>500</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>11&#160;400</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y en la plataforma 2 el costo es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2600</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8600</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>11&#160;400</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>8600</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, ambos cobros no son iguales.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Igualar los costos de ambas plataformas</strong></p>
            <p>Como se busca la cantidad de películas para la cual ambos cobros son iguales, se plantea:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msub><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msub>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:msub><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1400</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>500</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>n</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2600</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>300</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>n</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Reunir términos semejantes</strong></p>
            <p>Restamos <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mi>n</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> en ambos lados:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1400</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>200</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>n</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2600</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Luego restamos <m:math><m:mn>1400</m:mn></m:math> en ambos lados:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>200</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>n</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1200</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Despejar</strong></p>
            <p>Dividimos ambos lados por <m:math><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>n</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>1200</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>200</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar en ambas expresiones</strong></p>
            <p>Plataforma 1:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msub><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msub>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1400</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>500</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1400</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3000</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4400</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Plataforma 2:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msub><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msub>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2600</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>300</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2600</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1800</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4400</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Ambas plataformas cobran <m:math><m:mn>4400</m:mn></m:math> pesos cuando <m:math><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La persona debe ver <strong>6 películas</strong> para que ambos cobros sean iguales. La alternativa correcta es la <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>